<!--slider split-->

## Getting Timing Info

</div>
</div>
<div class="segment_container">
<div class="segment">

<!--slider row-split-->

> [C-style functions from \<time.h\> aka \<ctime\> ](https://en.cppreference.com/w/c/chrono)
> 
> - `clock_t clock()`
> - `time_t  time()`
>
> [UNIX-style functions from \<unistd\>](https://linux.die.net/man/7/time)
> - `time_t time(time_t *t)`
> - `int ftime(struct timeb *tp)`
> - `int gettimeofday(struct timeval *tv, struct timezone *tz)`
> - `int clock_gettime(clockid_t clk_id, struct timespec *tp)`
</div>
<div class="segment">

<!--slider cell-split-->
>
> [C++-style classes from \<chrono\>](https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/chrono)
> 
> - `system_clock`
> - `steady_clock`
> - `high_resolution_clock`
> - `utc_clock`
> - `tai_clock`
> - `gps_clock`
> - `file_clock`


</div>
</div>
